title: Air Lease Corporation Announces the Delivery of One New Boeing 737-800 to American AirlinesTravelandtourworld.com
text:
Air Lease Corporation Announces the Delivery of One New Boeing 737-800 to American Airlines
Air Lease Corporation announced the delivery of one new Boeing 737-800NG on long-term lease to American Airlines on August 14, 2015.
“ALC is very pleased to announce the lease of this new Boeing 737-800 to American Airlines, a new customer for ALC and a leading airline of the world. We look forward to a long-term relationship with American as they continue to renew and modernize their fleet and ALC expands its US presence,” said Steven F. Udvar-Házy, Air Lease Corporation’s Chairman and Chief Executive Officer.
Source:- Air Lease Corporation
